subject: Olympic Games (2008)
Track and Field
lead_paragraph: Allyson Felix is trying to become her sport’s dominant multi-event athlete, hoping to qualify to race the 100, the 200 and the 4x100 and 4x400 relays in the 2008 Beijing Olympics.
